  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Septic System Assessment and Rehabilitation for TY Yolanda Affected Communities in Ormoc, Leyte</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ASDSW will implement the ff. activities and expected outputs:
- assessment of the sanitation facilities of the 168 shelter units in Ormoc, Leyte and produce an assessment report of the piping system, septic tanks, leach fields or outlet pipes to the municipal sewage system and how these comply with the sanitation code and possible contamination of water sources; and,
- actual construction/rehabilitation of sanitation facilities based on the assessment recommendations that ASDSW and CA will agree to.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Contamination of water sources from unsealed septic tanks mitigated.</narrative>
  </description>
